data.description: We hear you! The home you have been looking for! A new roof, garage doors, and smooth top range. The primary suite is on the main, the house does not touch the neighbors, and there is a large yard with a privacy fence. This one-owner home has been well maintained and still outshines new construction compared to space, location, and school zone. This four-sided brick home is priceless. It has endless upgrades that are timeless. Wrought iron spindles on the staircase, two fireplaces, and a covered screen porch to relax on those summer evenings. Three-car garage and extra parking pad for your guests and additional family members. Do you want more for less or less for more? See this well-kept home and the community where all homeowners take pride and maintain their property. Hurry, home warranty!
